title: Extra large
description: Use this size sparingly and never multiple times on the same page.undefinedundefined

title: Large
description: Use for display text that’s more important than the medium size, but less important than extra large.

title: Medium
description: Use for display text that’s more important than the small size, but less important than large.undefinedundefined

title: Small
description: Use for text that would otherwise use body text, but that needs to scale with other display text.
